An example with ShowOff and Heroku. You can visit http://gentle-mist-369.heroku.com/ to run the example.

Additionally you can install a server to run it.
1.- Install gem bundler: $ gem install bundler
2.- Install the bundle: $ bundle install
3.- Create a directory and the structure
4.- Go to this directory (cd...)
5.- Run showoff serve
 Now you can visit the site in http://localhost:9090

If you decide to work with Heroku:

0.- heroku create
1.- git add <files>
2.- git commit -m "Message"
3.- git push heroku master 